{"tid":1699231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"他出發找最愛 今天也未回來 留低哪種意義 就看世間怎記載","createTime":"2019-11-08T03:24:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T09:34:48.000Z","uid":13663,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6d047de717d7b59ebe269310bc739a231086a123","tid":1699231,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T03:24:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/javtTCF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjavtTCF.jpg&h=e5af354e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c25e3fbf33ede46f81ea18284c293801661377b","tid":1699231,"uid":231090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T03:25:07.000Z","msg":"係街見到喊左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8500125e5076194b839ebe2021631f014b82c1f","tid":1699231,"uid":164838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T03:26:21.000Z","msg":"眼淚在心裡流<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf78afa8e37f76b6e8e06eeddc9ea1b26080469f","tid":1699231,"uid":304321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T03:26:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc37458d0d63bb9f92c8fb76c9fca804d9da2571","tid":1699231,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T03:28:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c13da98b3266008371c89bed08f2d43315e454","tid":1699231,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:01:36.000Z","msg":"科大學生周梓樂今天早上逝世，科大學生會及市民都發起悼念活動，資訊整合如下，由於活動正不斷更新，請持續留意最新資訊。<br />\n<br />\n1. 中午時段<br />\n科大學生會呼籲下午1點大家在各自位置默哀，而網上有不同地區自發午餐時段快閃，集合地點分別有朗豪坊、時代廣場、遮打花園、觀塘駿業街遊樂場等。<br />\n<br />\n2. 今天下午5點在觀塘海濱的中學生集會會加插悼念環節。<br />\n<br />\n3. 科大學生會正籌備今晚6點在科大舉辦燭光晚會。<br />\n<br />\n4. 有網民發起今晚8點到將軍澳尚德停車場進行悼念，呼籲自備蠟燭。<br />\n<br />\n5. 有網民發起，今晚8點在各自位置進行悼念， 亦有人發起同樣時間在18區開花。<br />\n<br />\nSource: 科大學生會發言、網上文宣"},{"pid":"a8124c8244792adcb55e4677ede482a2176926d1","tid":1699231,"uid":80503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:03:31.000Z","msg":"誰若碰到這個他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77d73197ce4864b8e232c58b7c3a59b4801ca600","tid":1699231,"uid":130698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:04:46.000Z","msg":"留下哪種意義 就看世間怎記載<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0c2200ca9860317c726a999854e17a7f2ec8ec","tid":1699231,"uid":19215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:09:06.000Z","msg":"首歌真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次聽到忍唔住喊"},{"pid":"87909ed6169caa0146b3c9a3499924774f92029b","tid":1699231,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T09:34:48.000Z","msg":"今晚見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}